  * Polish,  by @SeeLook (#2735)
  * Portuguese Brazilian, by @melcon (#2728)
  * Portuguese European, by @melcon (#2747)
  * Slovak, by @jose1711 (#2732)
  * Spanish, by @ignotus666 (#2706)

